title: Valencia v Real Madrid, LA LIGA LIVE score | Daily Mail Online
text: Real Madrid are in La Liga action on Wednesday as they make the trip to Valencia Victory for Zinedine Zidane's side will take them four points above Barcelona The fixture is one of two games in hand that Real have over their rivals Real Madrid: Navas; Carvajal, Ramos, Varane, Marcelo; Casemiro, Modric, Kroos; James, Benzema, Ronaldo Valencia: Alves; Cancelo, Garay, Mangala, Gaya; Parejo, Perez; Munir, Orellana, Nani; Zaza The match at Mestalla is due to kick off at 5.45pm GMT
